{"tid":1534330,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"2019-9月覺醒香港人注意事項","createTime":"2019-09-03T03:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T03:58:43.000Z","uid":205756,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e6c9210229417b7019ae5f0c8a5e3b57ea42b200","tid":1534330,"uid":205756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:25:51.000Z","msg":"&mdash;&mdash;不左膠&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n任何時候藍屍出手打我地手足先就要還拖<br />\n邊個做左膠就打埋一份<br />\n仲有捉到落單狗，唔好再咁左膠放佢走<br />\n你自己做左膠拎光環，班前線比狗打到頭破血流，你個良心去左邊啊？<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;不送頭&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n任何手足都好重要，打遊擊，不陣地<br />\n不圍狗屋 唔好留戀形式化嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;不捉鬼&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n唔好作出多餘嘅捉鬼行動<br />\n捉到又放鬼走，捉黎做咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上為發夢時所夢見的"},{"pid":"66dcd5940f149785ad33b144806b63059f93292b","tid":1534330,"uid":205756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:26:15.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"aa8f512342ea0001e1e0c670bba9420942c314fb","tid":1534330,"uid":205756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:26:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43e4bb7a0453d49692fccdecc89a8082a35df50f","tid":1534330,"uid":205756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:26:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fed8c4b3fce2c96f489d759e537e87a4805813cf","tid":1534330,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:27:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc4e8c4ece10afa74adaf70c37db89f753bbeab5","tid":1534330,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:27:42.000Z","msg":"9月必須進化<br />\n唔係唔洗打落去"},{"pid":"b888453029e5744df47164342fa557c4251a25b8","tid":1534330,"uid":205756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:27:50.000Z","msg":"9月8！到時見